                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The aurocan drops to 0 HP</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The aurocan detonates. Every creature in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:30] takes @Damage[3d12[bludgeoning],3d8[fire]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:23|basic] save). On a critical failure, a creature is also knocked @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone].</p>"
                },
